{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es pasihstu to / ka faudſeschu es wiſſu to Weeti winſch fanweim Behrneem/ un fa- winno labbad.\nwan Namman pehz ſewim pa-\nwehſehs/ ka tee ta KUNGA Zet-\nfarga/ darridami / kas taiſns\nun teefa irr / ka tas KUNGS\nleek nahkt us Ahbraimu / fo\nwiſsch us to irr runnajis."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija : Sodomas un Gomorras Breht- fchana irr leela/ un winno Greh- ki tohti gruhti."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad no-eeschn es un luh- kofchu / Arrig tee pehz tahs Brehtfchanas/ kas preeſſch man nahkuſi wiſſnotat irr darrijuſchi/ jeb ne ? tad es gann finna- ſchu."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Wihri greeſahs no turrenes/ un gahje uhs Sodo- mu/ bet Ahbraims stahweja wehl preeſſch ta KUNGA."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraims peegahje un fazzija: Arrig tu to Taifnu famaitaſi ar to Besdeewigu?"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jafchu peezeſſinitz Tai- fni irr Pilſſahta / arrig tu tohs famaitaſi/ un ne faudſefi to Wee- tu to peezeſſinitz Taifno deht / fas Pilſſahta irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Muhscham tu ta ne dar- risi/ nonahivedams to Taifnu ar to Besdeewigu / ka tas Taifns buhtu/ it ka tas Besdeewigs/ ne muhscham/ woi tas wiſſas Pa- faules Sohgis ne buhtu pareiſi teefaſis."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS: Ja es Sodomas Pilſtahta peezeſſinitz Taifmus atraddischu/ tad"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbraims atbildaja un fazzija: Rangi jelle/ es esmu eedrohſchinajees ar to KUNGU runnaht/ jepſchu es esmu Put tekſti un Pelni."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jafchu tur truhks peezi ne teem peezeſſinitz Taisnem/ bub- tu tu ſcho peezo deht to wiſſu Pilſſahtu famaitajis / un wiſſch fazzija : Es to ne famaitaſchu/ ja es tur tschetrdeſſinitz un peczue atraddischu."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad runnaja tas jo proh- jam us winnu/ un fazzija : Ja- ſchu tur taps tschetrdeſſinitz atra- ſti/ un wiſſch fazzija: Es nene- ka darriſchu to tschetrdeſſinitz lab- bad."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija: Ne ap- skaistees/ luhdsams/ KUGNS/ ka es wehl runnajit / jafchu tur taps trihsdeſſinitz atrasti. Un wiſſch fazzija: Es to ne darri- ſchu/ ja es trihsdeſſinitz atrafchu."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija: Rangi jelle/ es esmu eedrohſchinajees us- to KUNGU runnaht/ jafchu tur taps diwideſſinitz atrasti / un wiſſch fazzija: Es tohs ne fa- maitaſchu tohs diwideſſinitz lab- bad."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija: Ne ap- skaistees KUNGS/ luhdsams/ ka es wehl weenreisi runnajit/ ja- ſchu tur taps deſſinitz atrasti/ un wiſſch fazzija/ es tohs ne famat- taſchu to deſſmitz labbad."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nogahje tas KUNGS peh"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
